</span></p><p class='default'>
Default value: <p>ARM_AWAY</p>
</p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='payload_arm_night' href='#payload_arm_night'></a> payload_arm_night</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>The payload to set armed-night mode on this Alarm Panel.</p>
</span></p><p class='default'>
Default value: <p>ARM_NIGHT</p>
